      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you want the pain to end, but I won't agree with the idea that vanishing would make things better, because the debt and legal notices would still follow you. The shame feels heavy right now, but it is a temporary reaction to a temporary crisis, not a permanent character flaw. You are stuck in a moment of crisis, but you are still alive and capable of making different choices than those who have already gone before you.",
